text: Instagram is an American photo and video-sharing social networking service owned by Facebook, Inc. As of January 14, 2019, the most liked photo on Instagram is a picture of an egg, posted by the account @world_record_egg, created with the sole purpose of surpassing the previous record of 18 million likes on a Kylie Jenner post.
